item.title: Pricing
item.dc:creator: joshuawhatmough
item.content:encoded:
[one_half] [/one_half] [one_half_last]

New Client Special

$150 New Client Special. For ALL hair lengths Your choice of: 1.unlimited foils 2.All over colour 3.Ombre Also includes a Gloss Toner, Strengthening and moisture Treatment Mask, Precision Style Cut & a Glamorous Blow Dry, Straighten or Curls to finish off your new Amazing Hair. Cureplex is also available in salon so there is no fear of damaging the condition of your hair. All of our Stylists are all highly experienced Seniors.
[/one_half_last]
[one_half] [/one_half] [one_half_last]

Hair Extensions

We use high quality Human Hair extensions. We offer Show Pony and Carla Lawson Hair Extensions. Types of Extensions we are qualified in are
  • I-tip (beaded and Shrinkie)
  • Skin weft tape
  • Tape
  • Hand Tied Weft
  • clip-ins also available
Call us on 47756395 to make an appointment for your free consultation for a quote. (no quotes will be given over the phone or via PM's)
[/one_half_last]

Thick or Extra Long Hair

$20-$40 Please note that an extra cost will incur for Thick and Extra Long Hair on some Services. A Quote is always Given before we start any service.

Treatments

$10-$50 We offer treatments from a basic moisture treatment to the structure complex anti breakage system

Pin ups and upstyles

$50-$90 All trials are the same price as the acual upstyle as we are proving the same service as on the day.

Kids cuts

$12-25 Kids cuts are up to grade 6

Curls only

$30-$70 Just want your Hair Curled? We offer full body curls or just the bottom if you wanted it softer

Colour correction remover

$115-$145 This includes a dry off Does not include the colour we then have to do 2 days after. Please come in for a consultation for any colour correction so we can give you an estimate.

Chemical and Keratin straightening

$420-$840 Consultation is needed for any quotes for these services. Prices include a style cut and finish

Blow dries/ straightening

$25-$50 Includes a wash also

Facial waxing and tinting

$10-$40.50 We offer facial waxing and tinting and also packages for beauty service please ask us for a price on packages

Toners

$20-$95 Toners are add one to your service on the day. If you are wanting just a toner as a single service these are under colours.

Foils

$10-$135 Offering panals- full head

Ombré/ Balayage services

A consultation is needed before a quote is given for Ombre/ Balayage.

All over glossy colour

$50-$95 Created perfectly for each Individual hair type and colour

Men's Cuts

$25-$35 All men's cuts include a wash and finish

Ladies Style Cuts

$40-$80 All our style cuts include a Wash and finish.

item.title: Stylists
item.dc:creator: joshuawhatmough
item.content:encoded:
[one_fifth][/one_fifth][four_fifth_last]
Meet Karlene - Owner and one of the Top Stylists here at Rendezvous hair & Beauty. In the salon, she always strives to create an environment in which her clients are at ease to express themselves and their ideas. Specializing in Hair Extensions, cuts and colours for both men and women. It is Karlene's goal to help every client find a style that is a true fit for their hair type, and one that the client can easily replicate at home. Over the years Karlene has had a lot of experience in different areas of the industry, cutting, up styles, re-texturizing and coloring but she continues to advance her skills and keep up to date with the latest trends with Exclusive & Advanced Knowledge and Training. In her 12 yrs as a Stylist, Karlene has worked in different Salons but as with any career, the more people you work with the more you learn. Karlene has been lucky enough to work with some great talents in this industry and with every experience she walked away with greater knowledge and sharper skills. After working for others for years, She then decided it was time to become her own boss and realized that it was time to move forward and open her own Salon and then that’s when the the doors of Rendezvous Hair & Beauty opened.
[/four_fifth_last]
[four_fifth]
Meet Sarah - Sarah has been a stylist for 8 years now and prides herself on making her clients feel renewed and refreshed after every salon experience. She focuses on every detail to create a polished, fresh look for her clients. She continues to create cutting edge styles by advancing her Talent and knowledge when ever she is able. Perfection is Sarah's only acceptable standard when it comes to hairdressing. She will undoubtedly accomplish any look you are going for. So, whether you’re looking for soft and sleek or bold and brilliant, Sarah is the stylist you want by your side.
[/four_fifth][one_fifth_last][/one_fifth_last]
[one_fifth][/one_fifth][four_fifth_last]
Meet Danielle - Danielle brings a positive upbeat attitude to the salon and is excellent with all hair types and styles for both men and women. She is consistently striving to exceed the customer’s expectations while making them feel comfortable in her chair. Danielle is truly passionate about hair and is always on top of the trends. It’s her personal goal to continue to grow and excel in her craft and to ultimately share all that she learned with her Clients. She stays updated on all the latest trends and places high value on listening and understanding her client’s needs. She is extremely passionate about making your hair it’s most fabulous, and prides herself in outstanding customer service. She specializes in colour, and just loves when someone wants a change. Whether you are looking for a great cut and color, or need the perfect look for your wedding, formal, or special occasion, you are sure to fall in love with your hair! Danielle would love to meet with you and she promises to make you love your hair again and again.
[/four_fifth_last]
[four_fifth]
We would like to introduce our newest Member to our Team, Scarlett!! Scarlett is very excited to join Karlene and her wonderful team at Rendezvous Hair and Beauty. Along with being a very bubbly, friendly and easy to talk to stylist, Scarlett truly loves every aspect of hairdressing, but her speciality lies in Beautiful Blondes. Scarlett thrives to give guests the best experience and make sure they feel welcome in the salon and not only communicate, but also educate on products and how to look after your hair at home. She looks forward to meeting all of you and welcomes any of her current clients to our prestige boutique salon. Welcome Scarlett!
[/four_fifth][one_fifth_last][/one_fifth_last]
[one_fifth][/one_fifth][four_fifth_last]
We would like to Welcome Monique to our wonderful Team here at Rendezvous Hair & Beauty. Monique is very passionate about her Clients, she strives to make sure each and every one is extremely well looked after and makes sure that her guests are very pleased with the end result of their hair but can also maintain and upkeep their amazing new look with ease. Monique understands how important it is to have a connection with your stylist so you are able to come in for a pleasant and easy to communicate appointment, as she knows how scary it can be to find that "perfect" stylist. Monique enjoys every aspect of hairdressing there is nothing she won't strive to achieve "perfection only" when it come to your hair. We welcome all Past clients of Monique's to come and enjoy your time here at Rendezvous Hair & Beauty.
[/four_fifth_last]
[four_fifth]
The warmest welcomes to Shari! Shari is a bubbly, friendly and easy to talk to stylist, She enjoys to for fill every clients needs and make them feel absolutely beautiful when they leave her chair. Shari can provide you with up keep information and also easy styling techniques for home. She thrives to give all clients the best experience in salon, help educate you on products and styling with what struggles you may have. Shari looks forward to meeting new clients and welcomes back any of her past clientele and making you feel special and relaxed Welcome Scarlett!
[/four_fifth][one_fifth_last][/one_fifth_last]

item.title: About
item.dc:creator: joshuawhatmough
item.content:encoded:
Welcome to Townsville’s prestige Hair salon, Rendezvous Hair & Beauty. We specialize in all style cuts, colours, foiling, ombre, hair extensions, Chemical Straightening, formals and weddings, facial waxing and tinting to the highest professional level, with our true specialty being Permanent Hair Extensions. Our mission is to ensure that you as a customer feel comfortable and relaxed as our techniques are performed by a very talented stylists using De Lorenzo Australian Made & Owned Products along with only the Best Quality Hair Extensions, ShowPony.
Rendezvous Hair & Beauty is dedicated to consistently providing high customer satisfaction by rendering excellent service, quality products, and constantly improving our facilities and products to provide the most rewarding Experience and environment available anywhere for the ultimate in client care.
If you have any queries about our treatments/ services or are unsure about anything please contact us on 07 4775 6395 and we will help you to answer any questions you have.
